1
00:00:03,264 --> 00:00:10,246
Hi everyone. Today I'll be talking to you about cuteness and why it's important.

2
00:00:10,846 --> 00:00:16,907
So let's start off with myself. My name is Jenny and I also go by Qdork on Twitter.

3
00:00:16,927 --> 00:00:21,889
I recently graduated from the NYU Game Center with a BFA in game design

4
00:00:22,189 --> 00:00:25,930
and I've been making games for around three years at this point.

5
00:00:27,010 --> 00:00:29,410
So here are some of the cute games I've made.

6
00:00:30,311 --> 00:00:32,651
Slam City Oracles is a commissioned game

7
00:00:32,691 --> 00:00:35,712
that I worked on with Jane Friedhoff

8
00:00:36,032 --> 00:00:37,752
for No Quarter in 2014.

9
00:00:38,292 --> 00:00:40,033
It's a game where you and a friend

10
00:00:40,193 --> 00:00:42,513
slam around and tear down this colorful world

11
